PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775574665
OL,3,CArtemis II on way back to Earth after
OL,4,Cbreaking deep space record
OL,6,FWhile the astronauts did not touch
OL,7,Fdown on the moon, the mission paves
OL,8,Fthe way for a future lunar landing and
OL,9,Falso lays the foundation to send a
OL,10,Fcrew to Mars.
OL,12,FNasa is planning to return a crew to
OL,13,Fthe lunar surface by 2028, after
OL,14,Fchartering another mission - Artemis
OL,15,FIII - in 2027.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
